<p>EasyTwitter it's a simple wrapper library for the new Web API of Twitter v1.1</p>
<p>&nbsp;EasyTwitter is under &nbsp;development. At this time it has basic operations like OAuth authentication and simple tasks with tweets and user info.</p>
